ZenPayroll, Inc. is a privately-held, venture capital backed provider of cloud-based, SaaS-delivered, payroll services. ZenPayroll offers what it claims is a simplified payroll processing service aimed at smaller businesses that do not have full-time accounting staffs. The company was founded by Edward
