This PrivCo private company report on ZenPayroll, Inc. provides a detailed ZenPayroll, Inc. company profile, consisting of ZenPayroll, Inc. financials, ZenPayroll, Inc. annual revenues, ZenPayroll, Inc. annual revenues, ZenPayroll, Inc. competitors or competitive position / products / services, ZenPayroll, Inc. founders, and more private company information on ZenPayroll, Inc.

ZenPayroll, Inc. summary:
ZenPayroll, Inc. is a privately-held, venture capital backed provider of cloud-based, SaaS-delivered, payroll services. ZenPayroll offers what it claims is a simplified payroll processing service aimed at smaller businesses that do not have full-time accounting staffs. The company was founded by Edward Kim, Joshua Reeves and Tomer London in 2011 and is based in San Francisco, California.

